  <title xml:lang="EN">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The First Solomon Islands Transition to Sustainable Growth Development Policy Operation</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1" xml:lang="EN">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The proposed operation focuses on two Program Development Objectives, namely i) strengthening fiscal management in the areas of debt management, cash management and budget management; and ii) strengthening the business environment through simplifying tax processes, fighting corruption and supporting more efficient payments systems.</narrative>
  </description>
